title: ComicPirates Weeklies Index (CPWI) (2012-04 - 2014-12) (N=109k)
description:
CONTAINS:         Plaintext contents listings covering all Weeklies (and Monthlies
                  and Annuals) posted from TPB's "shipJ" and TPB's as well as KAT's
                  "shipjolly" accounts, corresponding to well above 90% of all
                  English comics releases that went through the "official" channels
                  during the stated period, plus a smattering of non-English ones.

DETAILS:          First = 2012-04-11   |   Last = 2014-12-31   |   Count = 109,382

FORMATTING:       The original data stems directly from the contents of the metadata
                  files (see  <a href=" https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/11728419" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/11728419</a>   ), and was
                  automatically processed into the following standardized format:

   |t>14-09-10 0000|s>  912,274,022|n>Spacehawk (2012) (Digital) (Bean-Empire).cbz

   t(imestamp)  - two digits each for year, month, day, hour, minute of release. The
                  last two are always 00, functioning only as placeholders here.
   (file)s(ize) - in bytes, formatted for improved legibility. Fixed-width field
                  with a 10-gigabyte maximum, which should suffice for a while yet!
   (file)n(ame) - including filetype extension

ORGANIZATION:     The three contained files are each sorted by a combination of two
                  of the three fields, as no single one of them is ever quite unique
                  by itself, due to chance, duplicate contents, identical naming, et
                  cetera. Specifically, by name then time (filename suffix "by nt"),
                  by size then name ("by sn"), and by time then name ("by tn")
